当被问及泰勒·斯威夫特的“折磨诗人部门”时，杰克·安东诺夫中断了采访https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-antonoff-cuts-off-interview-when-asked-about-taylor-swifts-tortured-poets-department-3610201?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jack-当被问及泰勒·斯威夫特遭受折磨的诗人部门时，安东诺夫中断了采访Liberty DunworthWed, 27 Mar 2024 15:48:31 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3610201 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰克·安东诺夫和泰勒·斯威夫特于 2023 年 2 月 5 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶 Crypto.com Arena 出席第 65 届格莱美颁奖典礼。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “如果您正在寻找点击诱饵，那么您来错地方了”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-antonoff-cuts-off-interview-when-asked-about-taylor-swifts-tortured-poets-department-3610201">当被问及泰勒·斯威夫特的“折磨诗人部门”时，杰克·安东诺夫中断了采访，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰克·安东诺夫和泰勒·斯威夫特于 2023 年 2 月 5 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶 Crypto.com Arena 出席第 65 届格莱美颁奖典礼。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，当被问及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>即将发行的专辑时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-antonoff">杰克·安东诺夫</a>突然结束了采访。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/bleachers-jack-antonoff-cover-interview-2021-take-the-sadness-out-of-saturday-night-3006942"><b>Bleachers：“这张专辑是关于想要保持快乐，而不是理解为什么你不能”</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手、词曲作者、制作人兼<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bleachers">露天</a>看台主唱正在与一家荷兰新闻媒体进行新的讨论，当时他被问及参与泰勒·斯威夫特即将发行的第 11 张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-new-album-the-tortured-poets-department-3582273">《The Tortured Poets Department》的情况</a>。</p><p>据包括<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/taylor-swift-tortured-poets-department-jack-antonoff-b2519212.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《独立报》</em></a>在内的多家媒体报道，这位音乐家在被要求谈论这位流行偶像的新材料后挂断了<em>NRC</em>记者的电话。据报道，他告诉媒体：“你知道我不会谈论这个。”</p><p> “如果您正在寻找点击诱饵，那么您来错地方了。感谢你们的这次谈话，”他补充道，并中断了采访。</p><p>然而，在采访的早些时候，安东诺夫确实谈到了他与这位“Bad Blood”歌手合作的时光，并探讨了他与 Bleachers 的合作与与 Swift 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a>的合作有何不同。</p><p> “我不认为它是在生产。我和朋友们一起创作音乐。它来了就来了。我不是那种在混音板后面发号施令的制作人。我让自己沉浸在音乐本身之中；引导创意过程的方式，”他说。 “能够很好地倾听彼此的声音是一回事。与我合作的艺术家相信我可以帮助他们让音乐变得更好。” </p><figure id="attachment_3610207" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3610207" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3610207" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff-Grammys@2000x1270.jpg" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特和杰克·安东诺夫于 2024 年 2 月 4 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶出席第 66 届格莱美奖颁奖典礼。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff-Grammys@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff-Grammys@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff-Grammys@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff-Grammys@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff-Grammys@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift-Jack-Antonoff-Grammys@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3610207" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒·斯威夫特和杰克·安东诺夫于 2024 年 2 月 4 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶出席第 66 届格莱美奖颁奖典礼。 （约翰尼·努涅斯/盖蒂图片社为唱片学院拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>虽然他在接受<em>NRC</em>采访时拒绝透露有关斯威夫特备受期待的专辑的任何细节，但他之前在二月份接受<a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/music/story/2024-02-28/jack-antonoff-taylor-swift-bleachers-lana-del-rey" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《洛杉矶时报》</em></a>采访时确实分享了自己的见解，透露他已经“完成”了《The Tortured Poets Department》的工作。</p><p>斯威夫特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-new-album-the-tortured-poets-department-3582273">在 2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼的舞台上透露了这张唱片的消息</a>，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/2024-grammys-winners-list-3582015">凭借《Midnights》获得了年度专辑奖和最佳流行声乐专辑奖</a>。除了获得年度专辑奖之外，安东诺夫还获得了年度非古典制作人奖。</p><p>两人已经合作了 10 年，他们的第一次合作可以追溯到 2014 年，当时他们联手制作了斯威夫特的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-1989-taylors-version-review-lyrics-tracklist-3522001">《1989》</a>专辑。</p><p>他们继续合作制作她接下来的五张录音室专辑—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-reputation-album-review-2158267-2158267">《Reputation》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-lover-review-2541084">《Lover》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-folklore-album-review-2713965">《Folklore》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-evermore-review-2835933">《Evermore》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-midnights-review-3332805">《Midnights》</a> ——并且还联手<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/taylor-swift-re-recordings-everything-we-know-3471197">重新录制了她第一张专辑的《（泰勒版）》。</a>四张专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3610208" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3610208" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3610208" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特于 2024 年 3 月 2 日在新加坡国家体育场举行的“泰勒·斯威夫特 | The Eras 巡演”中表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3610208" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在“泰勒·斯威夫特 | The Eras Tour”将于 2024 年 3 月 2 日在新加坡国家体育场举行。 （摄影：Ashok Kumar/TAS24/Getty Images for TAS Rights Management）</figcaption></figure><p> 《The Tortured Poets Department》将于 4 月 19 日发行，虽然细节仍然很少，但斯威夫特已经<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-the-official-tracklist-for-taylor-swifts-the-tortured-poets-department-3583090">分享了专辑的完整曲目列表</a>，并确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/post-malone-and-florence-the-machine-to-feature-on-taylor-swifts-the-tortured-poets-department-3583153">波斯特·马龙 (Post Malone) 和 Florence + The Machine 将会客串该专辑</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-tortured-poets-department-final-variant-3595989">这张专辑的多种变体也已经发布</a>——每一种变体都包含一首额外曲目——这位流行偶像还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-says-writing-new-album-the-tortured-poets-department-was-a-lifeline-3589651">告诉歌迷，创作这张专辑对她来说就像是“生命线”</a> 。</p><p>在杰克·安东诺夫的其他新闻中，最近有消息称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bleachers-announce-2024-uk-and-european-shows-including-brixton-academy-gig-3601155">Bleachers 将开始一系列英国和欧洲巡演</a>，定于今年秋天开始。这位主唱将于 2024 年下半年前往英国、德国、法国和荷兰进行现场演出，以支持乐队最新的录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/bleachers-review-jack-antonoff-3595341">《Bleachers》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-antonoff-cuts-off-interview-when-asked-about-taylor-swifts-tortured-poets-department-3610201">当被问及泰勒·斯威夫特的“折磨诗人部门”时，杰克·安东诺夫中断了采访，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
